Description:
Warm Family Starter In Prime Location!
Located near Derrimut Village shopping centre, this residence makes use of space with its expansive open planned living. If you are seeking a mixture of convenience, affordability and contemporary style then look no further; this property offers it all and more! Accommodation on offer includes three bedrooms plus study, two bathrooms, lock up garage, and open plan dining and family area adjacent a well equipped kitchen. Three bedrooms including main bedroom with walk in robe and en suite.
Second and third bedrooms each fitted with built in robes.
Stylish and functional kitchen, pantry and island bench ideal for casual meals or meal preparation.
Large tiled open plan dining and family area that offers plenty of space for everyday living and entertaining. Quality features including single remote garage, main bathroom with shower and bath, ducted heating, split system air-con, neutral colour scheme, front landscaped, and lots more! Located about 18km from Melbourne's CBD, this home is conveniently located near parks and playgrounds, childcare and schools. An inspection is a must.
